{
  "stem": "13238.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But the man was human.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "His approach was completely different than anybody what we knew before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "We were working during the seven months for him, hoping one day, we'll survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Because each and every time he came up, he always had a few nice words, kind words, to each and every one of us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And we felt very good to be under his protection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "There were a number of things what was going on during that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "One of the men was trying to get [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] rid of him was a top man of the SS men.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "He was the commandant of the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "His name was Oberster Fuhrer Leopold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Leopold was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And he was trying to liquidate the whole camp, in order to shoot in every-- every one of us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And when he-- when Oskar Schindler find out about his approach, he was trying to get rid of him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And one day, they were drinking very heavy-- Oskar Schindler and this Commandant Leopold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "He gave him [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] like a bomb, to throw on one of the garages there, what we didn't use.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "That's what he did, he was drunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "Immediately, he notified Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And they sent out this SS man from the camp, because he felt he could be danger to our survival.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "He did the utmost, in order for us to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, was bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when we arrived, the camp wasn't ready to absorb so many people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now this was a factory, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the bunks weren't ready.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to sleep on concrete floors, where water was running on the floors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we didn't have any other alternative.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were happy to have this, but just to stay with Oskar Schindler, his camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
